---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Operator Quickstart - CyberAi Documentation">
  <main class="docs-page">
    <div class="docs-container">
      <h1>üöÄ Operator Quickstart</h1>
      <p>Get started as a CyberAi operator in minutes.</p>
      
      <h2>Step 1: Access the Console</h2>
      <p>Navigate to the <a href="/operators">Operator Console</a></p>
      
      <h2>Step 2: Review System Status</h2>
      <p>Check GitHub Actions, contracts, and agent status</p>
      
      <h2>Step 3: Monitor CI/CD</h2>
      <p>View workflow runs and build status</p>
      
      <h2>Step 4: Access Runbooks</h2>
      <p>Follow operational procedures in the <a href="/docs/runbook">Operations Runbook</a></p>
      
      <p><a href="/operators">‚Üê Back to Console</a> | <a href="/docs">Documentation Home</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  .docs-page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
  .docs-container { padding: 2rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--neo-primary); }
  h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem; color: var(--neo-accent); }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #555; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  a { color: var(--neo-primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
